# Engine CLI cheat sheet — run these from backend/ (cd backend first),
# or use `make run EXERCISE=<name> VIDEO=<file>` from the repo root.
# ('c' = webcam, 's' = save the rendered output to output/videos/)

python -m src.main biceps_curl c
# Run biceps curl using your laptop webcam (without saving).

python -m src.main biceps_curl c s
# Run biceps curl using your laptop webcam and save the recorded output stream.

python -m src.main biceps_curl biw2.mp4
# Play a video file (without saving).

python -m src.main biceps_curl biw2.mp4 s
# Play a video file and save the output stream.

python -m src.main biceps_curl c → Run biceps curl using your laptop webcam (without saving).

python -m src.main biceps_curl c s → Run biceps curl using your laptop webcam and save the recorded output stream.
python -m src.main biceps_curl biw2.mp4 → Play a video file (without saving).
python -m src.main biceps_curl biw2.mp4 s → Play a video file and save the output stream.
